<template>

    <button @click='logout'>Log Out</button>
    <button @click="changeAddButtonMode()">Add Blog</button>
    <add-blog v-if="this.addButton"><button @click="changeAddButtonMode()">close</button></add-blog>

    <section>
    <single-blog v-for="blog in blogs"
    :key='blog.id'
    :id='blog.id'
    :from='blog.from'
    :createdAt="blog.createdAt"
    :title='blog.title'
    :content="blog.content"></single-blog>
    </section>
</template>


<script>
    import AddBlog from './AddBlog.vue';
    import SingleBlog from './SingleBlog.vue';
    export default {
        created()
        {
           this.$store.commit('retriveState'); 
        },
        components:{
            AddBlog,
            SingleBlog
        },
        data(){
            return{
                addButton: false,
                blogs: [
                    {
                        id: 'a1',
                        from: 'abc@abc.com',
                        createdAt: "2020/10/12",
                        title: "hello",
                        content: "hello everyone, meeting you on this time is my pleasure. This is My first Blog. Read it and enjoy it.",
                    },
                    {
                        id: 'a2',
                        from: 'abc1@abc.com',
                        createdAt: "2021/10/12",
                        title: "hi Man",
                        content: "hello everyone, meeting you on this time is my pleasure. This is My first Blog. Read it and enjoy it.",
                    },
                ],
            };
        },
        methods:
        {
            logout()
            {
                this.$store.dispatch('logout');
            },
            changeAddButtonMode()
            {
                this.addButton = !this.addButton;
            }
        }
    }
</script>
